DOC_LEVEL: L1
MODULE: project-config
PATH: package.json,.env.example,.codebuddy/settings.json,CODEBUDDY.md
DESCRIPTION: runtime dependencies, environment contract, and AI workflow rules

MANIFEST:
- package.json scripts: start, dev
- dependencies: dotenv, express, pino, screenshot-desktop, telegraf, zod

ENV_CONTRACT:
- telegram: TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN, ENABLE_TELEGRAM, ALLOWED_USER_IDS
- codebuddy bridge: CODEBUDDY_BIN, CODEBUDDY_PERMISSION_FLAG, CODEBUDDY_ECHO_STDIO, CODEBUDDY_HEARTBEAT_MS
- web: WEB_HOST, WEB_PORT
- system exec: ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC, ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES, SYSTEM_EXEC_TIMEOUT_MS

PLATFORM_SETTINGS:
- .codebuddy/settings.json -> UserPromptSubmit reminder hook present
- CODEBUDDY.md -> PrizmKit protocol section already present

DEPENDENCY_HEALTH:
- outdated_major: dotenv, express, zod
- npm_audit_prod: 0

